OL,5, Firefighters have warned people not to 
OL,6, follow a TikTok trend for building     
OL,7, makeshift heaters from tealights and   
OL,8, pots following a flat fire.            
OL,10,FAbout 50 people had to be evacuated    
OL,11,Ffrom their homes when the blaze broke  
OL,12,Fout at Prosperity House in Gower       
OL,13,FStreet, Derby but nobody was injured.  
OL,15,FIt emerged the fire had been caused by 
OL,16,Ftealights being used to heat terracotta
OL,17,Fpots.                                  
OL,19,FThe fire service said it strongly      
OL,20,Fdiscouraged the money-saving "hack".   
